overview: It is hard to properly move a household or business without a set plan and schedule. Without a plan and moving schedule your items could be a risk of getting damaged or delayed. Our local moving company completely understands that our customers have worked hard for their priceless valuable possessions. Local Movers Sunrise has constructed an effective procedure to securely pack, load, unload and settle all your items into your new location. We have specially designed our boxes with thick double width material to protect your items during your move. Customized bubble wrap, blankets and foam wrap are what our local movers use to fully protect your furniture from being scratched, damaged or scuffed.
